reviewText: For those who like custom bikes that aren't the overdone, trite, "triple-chrome-billet-fishing-lure" bikes that hacks like the clowns at OCC make, this is a great video. Roland Sands is an extremely talented designer and his projects are incredible. Not only is he good with a wrench, he uses high-tech design tools to create his machines. This video gives a great, in-depth look at all aspects of designing the bike.
